<h2>Global Assessment Report on Risk Reduction</h2>
<h4>Inventory of losses for Latin America, Asia and Africa</h4>

<p> In this place are available the historical inventories of losses that
were used in the project "Analysis of risk by extension".</p>

<p>The aim of this project is to provide inputs for the Report World
Evaluacion about the reduction of risks of the International Strategy for
the Reduction of Disasters.  That will be published in 2011 in Latin America
(Argentina, Bolivia, Colombia, Costa Rica, Chile, Ecuador, El Salvador,
Guatemala, México, Panamá, Perú y Venezuela).  Seven from Asia (Jordania,
Indonesia, Irán, Nepal, Orissa-India, Tamil Nadu-India y Sri Lanka) and one
from Africa (Mozambique) that were built both by governamental and non
governamental institutions.</p>

<p>The losses that were registered in the inventories are associated te
geologycal phenomenon, hidrometereologycal and fires.</p>

<p>The results of this project are added to the one made en the 2009 report
in which a first approximation to risks by extension is showed in 8
inventories of Latin America (Argentina, Bolivia, Colombia, Costa Rica,
Ecuador, México, Perú y Venezuela) and five of Asia (Irán, Nepal,
Orissa-India, Tamil Nadu-India y Sri Lanka).</p>

<p>This report can be consulted in <a href="http://www.preventionweb.net" target="_blank">http://www.preventionweb.net</a></p>
